data.description: Welcome to your dream starter home in Cottonwood! This charming home offers everything you need and more, making it the ideal place to begin your homeownership journey. With 4 bedrooms, there's room for everyone. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated main floor. New flooring adds a touch of style to every room, while fresh trim complements the home. The updated windows not only enhance the visual appeal but also contribute to energy efficiency, allowing natural light to flood the space. Car enthusiasts/hobbyists will rejoice at the sight of the nearly 1,000 sq ft heated garage. Whether you need space for multiple vehicles, a workshop, or storage for your outdoor gear, this garage has you covered. Enjoy the great outdoors right in your backyard! This home offers plenty of outdoor space, perfect for entertaining guests, hosting barbecues, or simply relaxing under the open sky. It's not just a house; it's a place where cherished memories will be made. Schedule a viewing today.
